{"article_id":"IdqSMa1D0fu1AtrM","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"FERGUSON Mo .","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"( ) -","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Residents of Ferguson , Missouri , prepared on Wednesday for a grand jury report","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"expected soon","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"on the fatal August shooting of an unarmed black teen by a white policeman , an event","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"that laid bare long-simmering racial tensions in the St. Louis suburb .","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"The shooting of 18-year-old Michael Brown sparked weeks of sometimes violent protests .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Many businesses have boarded up their windows","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"as they expect another wave of demonstrations to follow the grand jury ' s decision ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"particularly if officer Darren Wilson is not charged .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"But Jimmie Matthews ,","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"who said","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"he had lived in Ferguson for half a century ,","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"he planned to protest the grand jury ' s decision","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"regardless of whether it brings charges .","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"\" Whatever outcome they have ,","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"we ' re going to be protesting .","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"Either way , the issues are the same , \"","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"said Matthews ,","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"who is black .","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"\" We feel","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"that we are not protected by anyone in the system . \"","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"More than two-thirds of the residents of Ferguson are black ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"but its mayor , police chief and most of its police department are white .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"Black residents of the town say","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"their conflicts with the police long predate Brown ' s shooting .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Missouri Governor Jay Nixon on Tuesday named a panel of 16 commissioners","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"to develop solutions to the deep-seated socioeconomic disparities in and around Ferguson .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"Despite the tensions , some in Ferguson have tried to carry on life as usual .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"A crew of city workers spent Wednesday morning","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"putting up Christmas decorations on the street","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"that is home to the Ferguson Police Department .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Activists say","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"that will be the first place","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"demonstrators assemble after the grand jury report .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"Missouri Governor Jay Nixon","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"( L )","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"greets Richard McClure","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"( R )","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"and Reverend Starsky Wilson , the co-Chairs of the Ferguson Commission ,","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"after introducing them in St. Louis , Missouri","depth":4},{"id":42,"text":"November 18 , 2014 .","depth":3},{"id":43,"text":"/Adrees Latif","depth":3},{"id":44,"text":"Officials have said","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"the grand jury is expected to make its decision by the end of the month .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"The Ferguson-Florissant School District told parents on Wednesday","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"that schools may close early or not open at all on the day","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"the grand jury ' s decision comes ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"with the decision based on when officials learn","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"the report is coming .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"Country singer Hunter Hayes ,","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"citing the state of emergency","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"declared by the governor ,","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"canceled a concert","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"scheduled for Thursday night at an arena on the campus of St. Louis University .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"Nixon has defended his decision","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"to declare the state of emergency ahead of the grand jury ' s decision ,","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"a move","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"some called heavy-handed ,","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"particularly given that protests in recent days had been peaceful .","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"The state of emergency allows the National Guard to deploy to the St. Louis area .","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"\" For him to put Missouri into a state of emergency ,","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"to me it ' s a declaration of war on the protesters , \"","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"a local activist and rapper","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"who goes by the name T-Dubb-O","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"said on a media conference call","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"organized by activists .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"\" We ' ll be treated as third-class citizens again","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"when this decision is released","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"and they don ' t like what we are doing . \"","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"St. Louis Mayor Francis Slay asked for 400 National Guard troops to be deployed to his city ,","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"to work in alternating 12-hour shifts at 45 locations around the city .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"\" We will not try to disrupt , minimize , or in any way impede our constituents ' constitutionally protected right","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"to assemble","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"and speak freely , \"","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"Slay wrote in a letter to the city ' s Board of Aldermen .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"\" Our primary missions are to keep people safe ,","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"protect property","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"and safeguard constitutional rights . \"","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"Troops have not been visible on the streets of Ferguson","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"since Nixon declared a state of emergency .","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"There are conflicting accounts of what preceded the Aug. 9 shooting of Brown ,","depth":5},{"id":83,"text":"with some witnesses contending","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"he had raised his hands in surrender","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"and others describing a struggle between the teen and Wilson .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":171,"left":127,"right":170,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":87,"right":126,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":87,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":120,"right":125,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":111,"right":119,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":107,"right":110,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":91,"right":106,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":90,"right":6,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":88,"right":89,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":88,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":93,"right":105,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":93,"left":7,"right":92,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":98,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":96,"right":97,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":96,"left":95,"right":13,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":95,"left":10,"right":94,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":97,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":99,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"}